title: 10 Questions About the 10 First-Year Head Coaches
description:
Sheil Kapadia and Nora Princiotti answer 10 questions about first-year head coaches, ranging from most likely to win coach of the year to most likely to go viral.

Hosts: Sheil Kapadia and Nora Princiotti
Associate Producer: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Conor Nevins
